oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Country Music Hall of Fame Medallion Ceremony
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Country Music Hall of Fame & Museum (Nashville, Tenn.); Metal photoplates; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color lobby card (brown on red) announcing the Country Music Hall of Fame Medallion Ceremony at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on May 5. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Country Music Hall of Fame logo and a woodcut of the Hatch Show Print logo.
